thread.title: BRIEF-AIA Group Says FY Annualised New Premiums US$6.09 Bln, Up 19 Pct

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-AIA Group Says FY Annualised New Premiums US$6.09 Bln, Up 19 Pct

organizations.name: brief-aia group says fy annualised new premiums

text:
Feb 27 (Reuters) - Aia Group Ltd:
* IN FY 28 PER CENT GROWTH IN VONB TO US$3,512 MILLION * FY ANNUALISED NEW PREMIUMS INCREASED BY 19 PER CENT TO US$6,092 MILLION
* SAYS 17 PER CENT GROWTH IN FINAL DIVIDEND TO 74.38 HONG KONG CENTS PER SHARE
* FY VONB MARGIN UP 4.1 PPS TO 56.8 PER CENT * FY IFRS OPERATING PROFIT AFTER TAX UP 16 PER CENT TO US$4,647 MILLION Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
